MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-1705. State ex rel. Clements v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 95APD08-1080. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal and cross-appeals from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal of the appeal and cross-appeals,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
